            <h3>Cadiz City’s Must Do List</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>1. Visit Lakawon Island Resort and other beaches in the City.</li>
                <li>2. Buy the City’s famous dried fish and fishcharon delicacy (awarded as best delicacy 2011 in the Pana-ad sa Negros Festival) for pasalubong.</li>
                <li>3. Commune with nature at Balay Alibangbang Farm Resort, Green Lagoon, and Little Jungle Resort.</li>
                <li>4. Try the exotic Buriring</li>
                <li>5. Go trekking at Pacol falls. Cadiz City hosts a number of waterfalls.</li>
            </ol>
